              "free_text": [
                " A counter telescope consisting of",
                "a silicon p-n junction diode preceded by a gas",
                "proportional counter with offset center wire.",
                "Pulses from the gas proportional counter (dE/dX pulses)",
                "and from the silicon counter (E pulses) are fed into a",
                "multiplier network, output pulses of the latter",
                "identify detected particles as protons, deuterons or",
                "alpha particles."
              ]
            }
